service.tut.pori.cawebsocket

Class Registration

  • java.lang.Object
    • service.tut.pori.cawebsocket.Registration

  • public class Registration
extends java.lang.Object
    Registration details for Task Finished Web Socket Service. Backend ids, task ids and task types work as filters, not giving any values equals to "accept all values". When using user id or anonymous task filter, the user must have the appropriate permissions to access these tasks. In practice this means that the user must be the owner/creator of the task or have extended user permissions (e.g. ROLE_BACKEND).
